[normal]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Borderline cases[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]“case with overwhelming importance to the individual" means a case which is not primarily a claim for damages or other sum of money and which relates to one or more of the following--
